  <brief_title>A Bioequivalence Study of Amlodipine Plus Losartan Versus Amlodipine and Losartan</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-dose, Randomized, Two-period, Two-treatment, Two-sequence, Crossover Bioequivalence Study of Amlodipine and Losartan Versus Two Co-administration of Amlodipine and Losartan in Healthy Caucasian Subjects</official_title>
