  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study Design :

      - A single center, open, randomized, single dose, two-period, two-treatment, two-sequence,
      crossover study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Primary Objective:

      - To assess the bioequivalence of combination oral formulation of amlodipine/losartan versus
      two co-administered products containing amlodipine and losartan
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
